text: Pörtschach am Wörthersee is a municipality in Klagenfurt-Land in the Austrian state of Carinthia. It is on the northern shore of Lake Wörth (Wörthersee). Pörtschach is known for its summer resort. == References == == Other websites == * Municipality website * Tourist website Category:Settlements in Carinthia (state)
title: Pörtschach am Wörthersee
